io.grpc

Class MethodDescriptor<RequestT,ResponseT>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.grpc.MethodDescriptor<RequestT,ResponseT>

  • @Immutable
public class MethodDescriptor<RequestT,ResponseT>
extends java.lang.Object
    Description of a remote method used by Channel to initiate a call.

    Provides the name of the operation to execute as well as Marshaller instances used to parse and serialize request and response messages.

    Can be constructed manually but will often be generated by stub code generators.
